t","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"If it possible a theme won’t have such semantic tokens of colors defined as not specified nor used in Figma.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Thus the value for these tokens will be “ouds-forbidden-color-value” as returned by the tokenator.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Thus if the token is still used, even if explained in the documentation it should not,","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"this special value won’t be successfully parsed as color and the app will crash like expected."}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"protocol"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"ColorSemanticTokens"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"ColorSemanticTokens"}]}}}